# Code of Conduct

We are committed to a respectful, harassment‑free community. Be kind. No hate speech, personal attacks, or harassment. Debate ideas, not people.

- Be respectful and professional
- Assume good intent; ask for clarification
- No discriminatory language or behavior
- No doxxing or sharing private information

Enforcement:
- Violations may result in content removal or account blocking from this repository and related community spaces.

Reporting:
- Report violations via a confidential Issue (mark as “private” if using security advisories) or contact via the website: https://specdriver.dev.
